Package de.flyndre.fleventsbackend.controller

Klasse EventController

java.lang.Object
de.flyndre.fleventsbackend.controller.EventController
@RestController @CrossOrigin @RequestMapping("/api/events") public class EventController extends Object
This Class is the Controller for the REST-API path "/api/events". It provides an interface regarding events.
Autor:
Lukas Burkhardt
